                    <h5>Carlos Ramírez</h5>
                    <p>Paciente que venció el COVID-19 tras 60 días en UCI.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#casosExitoCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon bg-dark rounded-circle"></span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#casosExitoCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon bg-dark rounded-circle"></span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

